T23	Option 4592 4692	reliance by a court on such statements in civil proceedings may raise an issue under Article 6 § 1 of the Convention
T24	Option 4746 4858	the Court does not find it necessary to also assess if the labour court in reaching its conclusion relied on evidence in violation of the right to a fair trial
